item.dc:creator: Admin
item.content:encoded:
Did you know the Genesis framework comes equipped with multiple page formats and column classes? This allows you unlimited possibilities when designing pages and laying out images, text, and call to actions. Open your imagine and you open the world of options.

Available Page Layouts

  • Content/Sidebar
  • Full Width Content
  • Sidebar/Content
  • Archive/Sitemap
  • Column Classes
Column classes are wonderful and they work. Column classes allow the non-programmer to get jiggy with their content and make the page and website their own.

item.title: Fine and Sandy Blazer in Noir (3x)
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Is that big project at work keeping you extra busy these days? You needn’t worry about projecting your best self at the office, so long as you’re wearing this tailored one-button blazer! Crafted from 100% cotton, this sand-ridge-hued jacket 'suits' all your fashion needs with open side pockets, a classic curved hem, and a silky-soft lining. No need to roll up your sleeves before a big meeting, because this blazer boasts already-ruched 3/4-length sleeves for a look that’s functional and fashionable.

  • Shell: 100% Cotton. Lining: 100% Polyester.
  • Shell fabric provides stretch. Lining fabric does not provide stretch.
  • Fully lined. Front button closure. Chest pocket is temporarily sealed with manufacturer's stitching. Hip pockets are temporarily sealed with manufacturer's stitching.
